Aiune 
Ah ia aiune   ê eli gharalak 
 fen inta u btamol ê 
A dnuni 
A ia dnuni  ma tssibune 
Mish naes u Ana ghei ale 
Lana arif ertah’ 
U Ana deir sauah 
U el  snin 
U el  snin u Ana deib  shô u hanin 
A izaraf bass el tari u minin 
